<dl id="n42014c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n42" href="#n42014c">N42 (VI.B.31)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n42all.htm#n42014c"> 14(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> absolution</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">The conviction of her sins is now immediately connected with the thought of a man with whom she will have to speak, and who will easily make everything right and pure in her soul by his absolution. <small> Chiniquy, <a name="CPWC" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CPWC"><cite title="source">The Priest The Woman and The Confessional</cite></a> (n.d.) 47</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
